  "3070560": {
    "name": "贫民窟导游",
    "steam_appid": 3070560,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070560/extras/bfe1b9d46cf01717ed7a16b2c3e02a70.avif?t=1755276651\" width=617 height=64 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070560/extras/4d2c7ba269d31fa47f573d1d36298713.avif?t=1755276651\" width=617 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >踏入秘密的贫民窟，耳语的谣言吸引了众多寻求财富和机会的女性访客，她们对潜在的隐藏挑战一无所知。在这个以叙事为驱动的角色扮演游戏中，你将扮演艾德，贫民窟的一名足智多谋的居民，扮演向导的秘密角色。艾德的任务是通过收集信息和从不同来源（如当地商店、旅馆、教堂和居民）获得的工具来招募并融合这些毫无防备的女性。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070560/extras/554d394ddfe05ff8b33503d745342ee3.avif?t=1755276651\" width=617 height=80 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070560/extras/cfbd42f3308b302d448b91bd0a22fb7a.avif?t=1755276651\" width=617 height=720 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070560/extras/87a81171bd98e3b91075177e8a38251f.avif?t=1755276651\" width=617 height=720 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070560/extras/c2e01538e00b25ced69b35631aac26be.avif?t=1755276651\" width=617 height=720 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070560/extras/d9c078c53433f76b92c3d89382de5207.avif?t=1755276651\" width=617 height=720 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070560/extras/3cde6717bfed92b08ac87919571211b0.avif?t=1755276651\" width=617 height=720 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070560/extras/74a64320720c91dbfe4328c3f49df410.avif?t=1755276651\" width=617 height=720 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070560/extras/b373fe1645c75a0fc96963f6deac6e6c.avif?t=1755276651\" width=617 height=720 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070560/extras/cdc17f11e0c8abfa7a4901d43150043e.avif?t=1755276651\" width=617 height=720 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070560/extras/60f7fdefebd515099a2a2309e9d79219.avif?t=1755276651\" width=617 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >穿梭于贫民窟，利用艾德的智慧和你的战略才能。从居民那里收集关键信息，并从工具店获取专业工具以助你征服。关键在于解读这些女性在对话中无意间泄露的短语——这些词语可以巧妙地为你所用。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >参与复杂的对话序列，每个词都至关重要。注意你的目标暴露的弱点和欲望，操纵对话以影响她们的决策。一旦被招募，这些女性将成为关键资产：从对抗敌人的战斗人员，到在热闹的旅馆工作，或融入贫民窟的社区活动。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070560/extras/aebcae8748bf09bb23388bbb455dee19.avif?t=1755276651\" width=617 height=80 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>对话系统：</strong> 在对话的每个招募阶段，关键短语将被突出显示。点击这些短语会显示使用获得的工具和收集的信息的选项。招募这些女性成为贫民窟社区的一员的结果取决于你与艾德的协助能力，通过正确的选择利用她们无意中透露的弱点。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>招募角色：</strong> 招募的女性将以不同的角色出现——从作为战斗员进行娱乐或抵御威胁，到在当地旅馆工作或参与贫民窟社区的各种活动。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>战斗系统：</strong> 在与敌人的战斗和竞技场中协助招募者，利用她们通过战斗获得的技能和能力，或在武器店升级她们的武器。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>角色场景：</strong> 在每个招募阶段、准备阶段，甚至在招募者战败时，体验特别的角色场景，丰富叙事和角色互动。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>回忆模式：</strong> 查看解锁的角色场景，重温游戏中的特殊时刻。</p></li></ul>",
